data.description: Welcome to this updated Beautiful & Spacious two-story home! This beauty offers two living areas, three car garage, one bedroom and full bathroom downstairs,  and three bedrooms (including the Master) and two full bathrooms upstairs. The living room/dining area has been updated for a wider open space. The kitchen has also been updated, providing an enlarged kitchen island giving you extra countertop space. The house is prewired for solar panels. The single garage is insulated in case you would like to convert it into a 5th bedroom! Expansive backyard ideal for outdoor entertaining and big enough for a pool! Outside patio has been extended with concrete all around the side, has a gas line setup for an outdoor grill, and much much more! This gem is ready to be yours!!
